Package: montyhall
Title: Simulate and Analyze the Monty Hall Problem
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Susan", "Threadgill", email = "sthread@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to simulate the Monty Hall game show problem,
 including game creation, door selection, and outcome evaluation.
 The package can be used to explore probability outcomes and
 demonstrate the benefits of switching doors.
Imports:
    dplyr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
